thread.title_full: California Casualty Auto and Home Insurance reviewed by John

author: John
title: John
text: My family and I have been with California Casualty about 40 years, I think. Not much need for interaction, thankfully, but when we have needed to, people have been polite, helpful, good follow through. Rates are good. It's insurance I don't have to constantly think about!
